&gt;&gt; I'm a school counselor and
I'm always using books to,

00:27:37.250 --> 00:27:37.450
you know, encourage the children.

00:27:39.250 --> 00:27:40.650
I've read your book the 100
Best Books For Children,

00:27:41.250 --> 00:27:43.716
and I agree with a lot of them and
there's one that wasn't in there.

00:27:43.250 --> 00:27:44.116
I was going to email
but now I can tell you.

00:27:45.250 --> 00:27:45.783
I think it's the Five
Chinese Brothers.

