&gt;&gt; Anita Silvey: Oh, yes, yes.

00:27:49.250 --> 00:27:50.250
&gt;&gt; I love that, and I
was surprised it wasn't.

00:27:51.250 --> 00:27:52.940
&gt;&gt; Anita Silvey: Yeah, when you only
have a, by the way 100 Best Books

00:27:54.160 --> 00:27:54.770
for Children was the most sadistic
book that I ever did because I love

